Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OP「HIBANA」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:10.50,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}産み落とされた孤独な世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:14.33,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}誰を信じて生きて行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.38,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人とは何か　闇とは何か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.30,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飢えたこの目で睨んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.39,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正気と忘我　くり返してる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:29.47,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}奈落の底で呼ぶ声響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:35.56,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}黄泉の路を漂う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:40.49,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}声にひかり差す
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.41,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}守りたいもの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.78,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}変わらないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:52.33,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}精霊転化　絆を強さに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:58.46,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦い続けよう　踠きながら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:07.76,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}崩れそうでも　両手広げ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:15.90,OP_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,480)}火花を散らし　宿命を背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:10.50,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}诞生于孤独的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:14.33,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}我该信任着谁活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.38,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何为人类  何为暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.30,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只得瞪圆饥渴的双目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.39,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清醒与忘我  不断重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:29.47,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,360)}听见奈落深处的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:35.56,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}飘荡在黄泉之路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:40.49,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}我的声音映照光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.41,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}想要守护之物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.78,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,240)}未曾改变过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:52.33,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,0)}精灵转化  化情谊为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:58.46,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一同奋战下去  只管坚持到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:07.76,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便摇摇欲坠  也要振臂高呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:15.90,OP_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,480)}火花灿烂迸放  身怀宿命前行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「夕闇のうた」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:18.03,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}光と影が手を取り駆け巡る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:23.28,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}夜の中で生まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:30.83,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}小さな手のひらからこの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:34.00,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}愛を届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:40.26,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}荒れ果てた空の下に咲く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:47.31,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}一番あかるい花びら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:53.52,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}笑いさざめいて君と行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:59.90,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}時の中を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:03.91,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}祈りのように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,0:23:07.45,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}天と土を結ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:12.66,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,960)\blur3}君がうたう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:37.02,ED_JP_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}静かなうた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:18.03,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}光影交织巡回之间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:23.28,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}你降生于夜幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:30.83,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}小小的手掌向着广大世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:34.00,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}播撒爱的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:40.26,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}荒天之下唯独绽放着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:47.31,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那一轮最明亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:53.52,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}欢声笑语中与你同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:59.90,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}走过时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:03.91,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}如同心愿一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,0:23:07.45,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}天地走向大同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:12.66,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,960)\blur3}只因你的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:37.02,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}静谧之歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
